00:14:24,566 --> 00:14:29,058
Mr. Fukuda in Nanae Town produces shiitake mushrooms of the size you see!

228
00:14:30,092 --> 00:14:31,692
Called "King shiitake" mushroom

229
00:14:31,958 --> 00:14:35,325
It is a hidden specialty of Hakodate!

230
00:14:35,350 --> 00:14:37,083
Now, how does it taste?

231
00:14:40,819 --> 00:14:44,286
So much of the fresh flavour remains

232
00:14:44,319 --> 00:14:45,852
(Muroya) Delicious!
