00:16:21,526 --> 00:16:28,026
(Narrator) Cross-border socializing
And encounters, and good drinks...

265
00:16:28,179 --> 00:16:30,712
make Hakodate nights fun!

266
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:35,811
