269
00:16:41,366 --> 00:16:43,575
For example, in front of this Kanamori warehouse cluster.

270
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:45,366
If you go up this hill, there's a church here.

271
00:16:45,391 --> 00:16:47,458
(Yoshida) The history is amazing, isn't it?

272
00:16:47,483 --> 00:16:49,416
( Mr. Fukaya )
A little Western excitement.

273
00:16:49,793 --> 00:16:51,693
...with an air of romance.

274
00:16:51,718 --> 00:16:53,984
